shows.title: Salma The serial killer
shows.description: A serial killer (also called a serial murderer) is a person who murders three or more people,[1] with the killings taking place over a significant period of time in separate events.[1][2] Their psychological gratification is the motivation for the killings, and many serial murders involve contact with the victims at different points during the murder process
